layout.title: overview
layout.Description: This portlet shows a general overview!

layout.title: upComingvisits
layout.Description: The list displays patients where you are either the Admitting, Attending, or Performing provider. The patients have been admitted but not discharged. There will be many cases where the performing provider is not known due to the data not being available at the current time.

layout.title: pendingbillableencounters
layout.Description: Claims that are not submitted because they are not locked, documentation is pending, or the billing office has not submitted. The data accessible is a day behind, therefore it is current up to 8a this morning. Once the claims are submitted than your RVU count can be updated.
